data.description: Motivated Seller....Priced below recent appraisal. Beautiful Custom-built home on almost 10 acres. Very private and very convenient to everything. Large home for a growing family or multiple families. Main level includes beautiful renovated kitchen very open floor plan, island, stainless appliances, custom cabinets with lots of counter space, separate dining room, Great room with massive stacked stone fireplace, master suite on main level with an oversized bathroom, walk in closet and separate shower and jetted tub, upstairs has two additional bedrooms a common area and two full baths, Basement features a full apartment or in law suite with its own entrance, Above the 3 car garage is a huge bonus room with its own bathroom. Also, a 3-car detached shop has a workshop and additional parking. Also, a great entertainment area behind the shop equipped with surround sound and a projector movie screen. Great for parties, family get togethers etc. Also, it has a parking shed for RV/ boat etc. Don't miss out on this great opportunity in highly desired school district.
